DESCRIPTION :

iGene has delivered more than 300 films in Hollywood, Europe, China, Singapore and India. iGene provides tailor made training which is exactly needed in production pipeline for creative and non-creative aspirants. iGene delivers skill guarantee in turn leading to job guarantee.

iGene is reaching out the students to create awareness and career opportunity in the field of VFX and also advanced industry based learning.
iGene School of VFX Technology focuses on creating production intensive manpower resources in the field of Visual Effects.

iGene School is a division of iGene Entertainment services private Limited. iGene is a leader in the field of Visual Effects and Animation, both in International and Domestic Market. Integrated learning for a more versatile workforce is the philosophy of iGene School. This approach of industry-oriented learning and hands-on production will help the students to nurture necessary skills to mould their professional-level portfolio. iGene believes in equipping candidates with the right skill set that the Production needs, that will enable them to get their dream job.
